 procedure\nimproves both the statistical significance and biological interpretability of\nthe results. In addition to achieving considerably lower false positive rates,\nour procedure shows better performance in detecting important biological\npathways.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 25 Jan 2014 08:07:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 1 Jun 2015 07:35:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-02"}
